snippet.title: Omega no sunshine 2 Gameplay (っ◔◡◔)っadditional map[end game]
snippet.description:
gameplay officiel : map additionelle
{date de sortie prevue au 9 aout 2024]
official gameplay from omega no sunshine
[planned release for august the 9th] -- Watch live at https://www.twitch.tv/ikowaifu

this video game named omega no sunshine is my own creation, the gameplay is in black and white
it was a choice of mine to not spoil the map
https://celestial-factory.itch.io/omega-no-sunshine-24
it'll be released here august the 9th for a soft price 2.99euros

Note : Omega no sunshine 2 is also called Omega no sunshine 2024
because,depending of player support i would deeply love to work on an another
game of this serie.or a yearly extension.
